"title": "8741: failure",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "8741",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Scripture indicates various ways in which believers may fail God, while emphasising that God will never fail his people.</p>\n<h2>God will never fail his people</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr28:20\">1CH 28:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh1:8-Josh1:9\">JOS 1:8–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:28\">PSA 89:28</a></p>\n<h3>God's righteousness will not fail</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa51:6\">ISA 51:6</a></p>\n<h3>God's compassion will not fail</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lam3:22-Lam3:23\">LAM 3:22–3:23</a></strong></p>\n<h2>God's word will not fail</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa55:10-Isa55:11\">ISA 55:10–55:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:6\">ROM 9:6</a></p>\n<h2>Examples of failing God</h2>\n<h3>Failing to abide in him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:3\">PSA 14:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps58:3\">PSA 58:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:57\">PSA 78:57</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:19\">JER 2:19</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer3:22\">JER 3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer15:6\">JER 15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John15:6\">JHN 15:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:17\">2PE 3:17</a></p>\n<h3>Failing to believe in him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John20:27\">JHN 20:27</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num14:11-Num14:12\">NUM 14:11–14:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:21-Ps78:33\">PSA 78:21–78:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:12\">HEB 3:12</a></p>\n<h3>Failing to fear him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen20:11\">GEN 20:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod9:30\">EXO 9:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:18\">DEU 25:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job6:14\">JOB 6:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:40\">LUK 23:40</a></p>\n<h3>Failing to honour him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal2:2\">MAL 2:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Num20:12\">NUM 20:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam2:29-1Sam2:30\">1SA 2:29–2:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan5:22-Dan5:23\">DAN 5:22–5:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:23\">ROM 2:23</a></p>\n<h3>Failing to love him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor16:22\">1CO 16:22</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh23:10-Josh23:13\">JOS 23:10–23:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt10:37\">MAT 10:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev2:4\">REV 2:4</a></p>\n<h3>Failing to obey him</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs17:14-2Kgs17:20\">2KI 17:14–17:20</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt7:26\">MAT 7:26</a></p>\n<h3>Failing to remember him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:11\">DEU 8:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut32:18\">DEU 32:18</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg3:7\">JDG 3:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg8:33-Judg8:34\">JDG 8:33–8:34</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam12:9\">1SA 12:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps78:11\">PSA 78:11</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps106:21\">PSA 106:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa17:10\">ISA 17:10</a></p>\n<h3>Failing to seek him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr12:14\">2CH 12:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps14:2-Ps14:3\">PSA 14:2–14:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:155\">PSA 119:155</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:13\">ISA 9:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zeph1:6\">ZEP 1:6</a></p>\n<h3>Failing to serve him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut28:47-Deut28:48\">DEU 28:47–28:48</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job21:14-Job21:15\">JOB 21:14–21:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer2:20\">JER 2:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:14\">MAL 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:25\">ROM 1:25</a></p>\n<h3>Failing to trust him</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:30\">MAT 6:30</a></strong> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:28\">LUK 12:28</a> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt14:31\">MAT 14:31</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:8\">MAT 16:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt17:17-Matt17:20\">MAT 17:17–17:20</a></p>\n<h3>Peter's failure of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:33-Matt26:35\">MAT 26:33–26:35</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark14:29-Mark14:31\">MRK 14:29–14:31</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke22:31-Luke22:34\">LUK 22:31–22:34</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John18:25-John18:27\">JHN 18:25–18:27</a></p>",
